<node id="TestState">
  <data key="d0">TestState</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An abstract concept representing the state of tests for different site codes, managing test execution and data.&lt;SEP&gt;Singleton class that manages the shared state for customer-related tokens and identifiers in the GRA testing framework.&lt;SEP&gt;A singleton class used for managing shared state with typed getters and setters, ensuring backward compatibility.&lt;SEP&gt;An isolated shared state per brand, managed through a map keyed by site code.</data>
