  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A footwear and apparel brand known for its casual and athletic shoes.&lt;SEP&gt;A brand that utilizes several third-party services for analytics and product recommendations, similar to other brands listed.&lt;SEP&gt;An international footwear brand that designs and markets a range of lifestyle and performance shoes.&lt;SEP&gt;A footwear and apparel company referenced in the context of preference in product selection for men's items.&lt;SEP&gt;A global footwear brand known for its athletic shoes, which requires specific navigation for its product detail pages.&lt;SEP&gt;Skechers is a footwear company offering a variety of shoes, including styles for men, women, and children. It has a specific focus on comfort and casual styles.</data>
