<node id="Vans NZ">
  <data key="d0">Vans NZ</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The New Zealand counterpart of Vans, which does not earn Qantas Points.&lt;SEP&gt;A counterpart to Vans AU, adhering to the same technical standards in the GRA storefront setup.&lt;SEP&gt;A New Zealand brand related to Vans AU, exhibiting distinct navigation properties.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific location related to the Vans brand, identified as Vans New Zealand. It potentially has a similar full-page acquisition popup as Vans Australia.&lt;SEP&gt;A regional branch of Vans, a footwear company, specifically mentioned in the context of product selection.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Zealand branch of Vans, which also faces navigation and interaction challenges on its ecommerce site.&lt;SEP&gt;Vans NZ is a footwear brand known for its skate shoes and casual footwear, particularly popular among youth and urban culture.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-18c320b704b53c1b59c41f904f29e640-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cecb0d91ce73637998acce9c5c61beac-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-92ee23296c45f454b040c61ea2ec6e86-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cecb0d91ce73637998acce9c5c61beac-chunk-001</data>
