<node id="Platypus AU">
  <data key="d0">Platypus AU</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Platypus AU is an Australian brand primarily focused on footwear, operating within Australia and New Zealand. The brand's retail presence includes a staging URL for e-commerce, enabling customers to purchase products while accepting Qantas Points for transactions. Platypus AU utilizes the Magento platform version 2.4.6-p15, implementing specific storage and cookie strategies tailored for its GRA storefront setup.

The brand is known for its unique navigation labels and incorporates various technologies for page recording and error tracking to enhance user experience. Additionally, Platypus AU plays a vital role in e-commerce testing, particularly concentrating on footwear within localization smoke tests, ensuring that the online storefront meets quality standards across different scenarios.

The physical stores under the Platypus brand are identified as Platypus Australia, which are part of a coordinated set of locations sharing a common data layer structure. Platypus AU’s functionality extends to checking for semantic landmarks, like headers, to ensure optimal content delivery and site performance.

Overall, Platypus AU represents a comprehensive retail e-commerce operation that combines technological innovation with a customer-focused approach in the footwear market.&lt;SEP&gt;Platypus AU is a retail organization that sells a wide range of footwear brands, including Skechers and Vans.&lt;SEP&gt;An Australian retail entity that encountered issues with the overlay implementation during concurrent testing scenarios.&lt;SEP&gt;An online retail store based in Australia, utilized for testing shipping method selections within the E2E-CHKOUT-004 project.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-18c320b704b53c1b59c41f904f29e640-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-92ee23296c45f454b040c61ea2ec6e86-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cf017a813cd0b782aef34bc894b9789d-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a74540e7570b89ad3bb5cb22795ee605-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cecb0d91ce73637998acce9c5c61beac-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cecb0d91ce73637998acce9c5c61beac-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-89278d88eec2b6ee50a522529e8ddbde-chunk-000</data>
