  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A brand specializing in skate shoes and related apparel, known for its distinctive style.&lt;SEP&gt;A footwear brand that applies multiple third-party services for fraud detection and analytics.&lt;SEP&gt;A global footwear company that has a strong presence in the market, known for its shoes and apparel.</data>
