<node id="Skechers AU">
  <data key="d0">Skechers AU</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-18c320b704b53c1b59c41f904f29e640-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-003&lt;SEP&gt;doc-c9488069466f7da02e04d0a79614e167-chunk-002&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cf017a813cd0b782aef34bc894b9789d-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cf017a813cd0b782aef34bc894b9789d-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-a74540e7570b89ad3bb5cb22795ee605-chunk-000&lt;SEP&gt;doc-cecb0d91ce73637998acce9c5c61beac-chunk-004&lt;SEP&gt;doc-89278d88eec2b6ee50a522529e8ddbde-chunk-000</data>
  <data key="d2">Skechers AU is an Australian footwear brand recognized for its e-commerce operations and physical retail presence throughout Australia. This brand is notable for accepting Qantas Points, enhancing its customer loyalty program. It showcases specific navigation labels on its website, aimed at providing a user-friendly experience for shoppers.

The brand uses a technology stack similar to that of Platypus, which has led to the identification of certain technical bugs, particularly in the layout of its PageBuilder. These issues include implementation quirks such as multiple header elements on web pages, with a significant number of these headers being empty. The homepage also reflects the same PageBuilder-Banner-root pattern found in its counterpart, Skechers NZ.

Furthermore, Skechers AU has been involved in localization smoke tests, ensuring that its storefront effectively caters to the Australian market. This entity further exemplifies the technical details shared by other eCommerce brands operating on similar platforms, indicating a broader shared infrastructural approach in the retail sector.&lt;SEP&gt;The Australian branch of the Skechers footwear brand, identified as one of the storefronts affected by timing issues related to the overlay state detection.&lt;SEP&gt;An Australian branch of the Skechers footwear brand, mentioned in relation to a previous field-pattern mismatch theory.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d4">ecommerce-storefronts.md&lt;SEP&gt;gra-storefront-tech-notes.md&lt;SEP&gt;ecommerce-smoke-spec-catalog.md&lt;SEP&gt;ecommerce-header-help-gotcha.md&lt;SEP&gt;ecommerce-pdp-page-gotchas.md&lt;SEP&gt;e2e-chkout-004-shipping-method.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1784615429</data>
