<node id="Playwright">
  <data key="d0">Playwright</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A testing framework used for automating browser interactions, particularly for testing web applications.&lt;SEP&gt;Playwright is an open-source automation framework for browser testing that allows for automation of web applications across various browsers.&lt;SEP&gt;A testing framework used for end-to-end testing of web applications, allowing automation of browser interactions.&lt;SEP&gt;A tool used for automating browsers, allowing for the execution of tests within different contexts and configurations mentioned in the project.&lt;SEP&gt;An open-source library used for browser automation, allowing testing across different browsers.&lt;SEP&gt;An open-source automation library for testing web applications across different browsers.</data>
