  <data key="d0">TypeScript 6.x</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">TypeScript 6.x is a version of the TypeScript programming language, held on version 5.x until the ecosystem stabilizes, which is expected to occur in Q3 to Q4 of 2026. It is associated with migration processes in TypeScript development.</data>
